Bash("""

import os
import sys
from datetime import datetime, timedelta
import psycopg2
import requests
from dotenv import load_dotenv

# Load environment variables
load_dotenv\(\)

# Database connection
DB_CONFIG = {
    ''host'': os.getenv\(''POSTGRES_HOST'', ''localhost''\),
    ''port'': int\(os.getenv\(''POSTGRES_PORT'', ''5432''\)\),
    ''user'': os.getenv\(''POSTGRES_USER'', ''sofia''\),
    ''password'': os.getenv\(''POSTGRES_PASSWORD'', ''''\),
    ''database'': os.getenv\(''POSTGRES_DB'', ''sofia_db''\),
}

def create_table\(conn\):
    """"""Create clinical_trials table if not exists""""""
    cur = conn.cursor\(\)
    cur.execute\(''''''
        CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS sofia.clinical_trials \(
            nct_id VARCHAR\(20\) PRIMARY KEY,
            title TEXT NOT NULL,
            brief_summary TEXT,
            condition TEXT,
            intervention_name TEXT,
            phase VARCHAR\(20\),
            status VARCHAR\(50\),
            enrollment_count INTEGER,
            start_date DATE,
            completion_date DATE,
            sponsor TEXT,
            study_type VARCHAR\(50\),
            keywords TEXT[],
            collected_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW\(\)
        \)
    ''''''\)
    conn.commit\(\)
    cur.close\(\)

def collect_trials\(\):
    """"""Collect clinical trials from ClinicalTrials.gov API""""""
    
    print\(''='' * 80\)
    print\(''CLINICALTRIALS.GOV COLLECTOR''\)
    print\(''='' * 80\)
    print\(\)
    
    # Connect to database
    try:
        conn = psycopg2.connect\(**DB_CONFIG\)
        print\(''âœ… Database connected''\)
        create_table\(conn\)
    except Exception as e:
        print\(f''âŒ Database connection failed: {e}''\)
        return
    
    # Technology/medical device related conditions
    conditions = [
        ''artificial intelligence'',
        ''machine learning'',
        ''digital health'',
        ''telemedicine'',
        ''medical device'',
        ''robotic surgery'',
        ''gene therapy'',
        ''immunotherapy''
    ]
    
    total_trials = 0
    
    for condition in conditions:
        print\(f''ðŸ” Searching: {condition}''\)
        
        try:
            # ClinicalTrials.gov API v2
            url = ''https://clinicaltrials.gov/api/v2/studies''
            params = {
                ''query.cond'': condition,
                ''filter.overallStatus'': ''RECRUITING,ACTIVE_NOT_RECRUITING,COMPLETED'',
                ''pageSize'': 50,
                ''format'': ''json''
            }
            
            response = requests.get\(url, params=params, timeout=30\)
            response.raise_for_status\(\)
            data = response.json\(\)
            
            studies = data.get\(''studies'', []\)
            print\(f''   âœ… Found {len\(studies\)} trials''\)
            
            cur = conn.cursor\(\)
            
            for study in studies:
                protocol = study.get\(''protocolSection'', {}\)
                id_module = protocol.get\(''identificationModule'', {}\)
                status_module = protocol.get\(''statusModule'', {}\)
                description_module = protocol.get\(''descriptionModule'', {}\)
                conditions_module = protocol.get\(''conditionsModule'', {}\)
                design_module = protocol.get\(''designModule'', {}\)
                arms_module = protocol.get\(''armsInterventionsModule'', {}\)
                sponsor_module = protocol.get\(''sponsorCollaboratorsModule'', {}\)
                
                nct_id = id_module.get\(''nctId'', ''''\)
                if not nct_id:
                    continue
                
                # Insert or update
                cur.execute\(''''''
                    INSERT INTO sofia.clinical_trials \(
                        nct_id, title, brief_summary, condition, intervention_name,
                        phase, status, enrollment_count, start_date, completion_date,
                        sponsor, study_type, keywords
                    \) VALUES \(%s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s\)
                    ON CONFLICT \(nct_id\) DO UPDATE SET
                        title = EXCLUDED.title,
                        brief_summary = EXCLUDED.brief_summary,
                        status = EXCLUDED.status,
                        collected_at = NOW\(\)
                '''''', \(
                    nct_id,
                    id_module.get\(''briefTitle'', ''''\)[:500],
                    description_module.get\(''briefSummary'', ''''\)[:1000],
                    '', ''.join\(conditions_module.get\(''conditions'', []\)\)[:500],
                    '', ''.join\([i.get\(''name'', ''''\) for i in arms_module.get\(''interventions'', []\)]\)[:500],
                    design_module.get\(''phases'', [''N/A'']\)[0] if design_module.get\(''phases''\) else ''N/A'',
                    status_module.get\(''overallStatus'', ''Unknown''\),
                    design_module.get\(''enrollmentInfo'', {}\).get\(''count''\),
                    status_module.get\(''startDateStruct'', {}\).get\(''date''\),
                    status_module.get\(''completionDateStruct'', {}\).get\(''date''\),
                    sponsor_module.get\(''leadSponsor'', {}\).get\(''name'', ''''\)[:500],
                    design_module.get\(''studyType'', ''N/A''\),
                    conditions_module.get\(''keywords'', []\)[:20]
                \)\)
                
                total_trials += 1
            
            conn.commit\(\)
            cur.close\(\)
            
        except Exception as e:
            print\(f''   âŒ Error: {e}''\)
            continue
    
    conn.close\(\)
    
    print\(\)
    print\(''='' * 80\)
    print\(''âœ… CLINICAL TRIALS COLLECTION COMPLETE''\)
    print\(''='' * 80\)
    print\(f''ðŸ’¾ Total trials: {total_trials}''\)
    print\(\)

if __name__ == ''__main__'':
    collect_trials\(\)
EOF
